[DhtmlXQ_open]A28 飞相转屏风马对左中炮[/DhtmlXQ_open]
[DhtmlXQ_remark]李中健、刘海亭[/DhtmlXQ_remark]
[DhtmlXQ_author]独来读网[/DhtmlXQ_author]
